Proud member of Rune of Flame</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/udonord.showPublicProfile?language=EN>donord</A> at: 12/11/00 8:27:36 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/usalamren.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Salamren</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>w4nn4b3!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(12/11/00 4:21:16 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://facelink.com/salamren?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How do YOU use CH?</span><hr size=1> Crippling blows are cool.<br>
